{"tid":159541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲仔家事困擾墮樓亡　母拭淚哭別兒子","createTime":"2017-03-17T05:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T12:26:46.000Z","uid":11030,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e89cb1f355b2ff80acb736e231fb737550f86e16","tid":159541,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"22歲仔家事困擾墮樓亡　母拭淚哭別兒子<br />\n03月17日(五)<br />\n08:44更新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/photo/bkn-20170317043746645-0317_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170317%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170317043746645-0317_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=a177f4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天水圍天瑞邨瑞財樓男子墮樓亡。凌晨4時許，保安員聽聞一聲巨響，發現一名姓羅(22歲)青年倒臥於2樓簷篷上，連忙致電報警。救護員到場證實羅當場死亡，消防到場協助將屍體移落大廈對開，警員用帳篷遮蓋屍體。<br />\n<br />\n死者母親聞訊到場協助調查，並於大廈外凝望遮蓋兒子遺體的帳篷拭淚。警員現場檢獲遺書，相信死者由梯間墮下，事件無可疑，據了解，死者因家庭問題不開心。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/bkn-20170317043746645-0317_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170317%2Fbkn-20170317043746645-0317_00822_001.html&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=2486a4d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/bkn-20170317043746645-0317_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"15f12570343a9a1246b0c8dbe850a262f8cae6e8","tid":159541,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"一日一件"},{"pid":"a89b2bb056a3d503b35c623e96497e2ba1ea0231","tid":159541,"uid":38816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人數到係第幾單，點解成個星期日日都有人跳樓"},{"pid":"240495244e013fb5fb765d10a6d41d95dd8055b4","tid":159541,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"